      <title>枪支制造商敦促美国最高法院审理墨西哥诉讼中的上诉</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/gun-makers-urge-us-supreme-court-hear-appeal-mexicos-lawsuit-2024-04-19/</link>
